      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i can't even find the point in trying anymore. like if you actually look at the scale of everything, we're just accidental blips. in a few billion years the sun dies, the universe goes cold, and none of this—none of the struggle or the pain or the work—ever mattered. it's all just a cosmic joke. why am i even putting in the effort to exist?",
